# Belt-and-suspenders: the root .gitignore already excludes everything in
# this directory except the three tracked files (.gitignore, README.md,
# CLAUDE.md). This nested .gitignore makes the rule survive even if the
# vendor/ tree is checked into a different repo, or if a contributor runs
# `git add vendor/` from inside this directory.

*
!.gitignore
!README.md
!CLAUDE.md
